These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, january, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Birthday         | december | october    | january      | february |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, billiard, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing whist is the fisherman##1
6. the person playing poker is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Game   | monopoly    | poker   | billiard     | whist      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, guinea-pig, cat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the cat is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the russian is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the owner of the hamster is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | hamster | goat | guinea-pig | cat |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, june, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday         | january | december | june | april |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

