.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo, sailing, rowing
1. the accountant is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the mechanic##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the writer is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Sport   | rowing   | climbing     | sailing | water-polo       |

