.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, mexican, russian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, march, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the british##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | indonesian | mexican | russian |
| Birthday         | august | july | october  | march  |
| Transport     | roller  | snowmobile | van     | subway  |

