3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | chess | writing | woodworking |
| Cigar         | dunhill | havana  | aristoff   | vegafina      |
| Transport   | car        | taxi  | trike   | bus         |

