.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
City: marseilles, new-york, hannover, berlin
1. the engineer is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| City         | marseilles | hannover    | new-york   | berlin         |

 